------------ MISC. FORMATTING COMMANDS ----------- ,PP      Paragraph ,PPNL N  Paragraph need N lines on same page ,PPSP N  Paragraph space N lines ,PPSI N  Paragraph single indent ,BFS  N  Boldface strike N times at printout ,PADC C  Pad char. C for non-pad spaces on print ,MMC  C  Mail Merge character C ,PC   C  Print char C to delimit print strings ,*       Comment line